name: Dustin Harper
review: This church provides sound biblical preaching and a friendly community of believers. The services are family integrated and highly reverential. Evening services and Wednesday night Bible studies are also held, and are great opportunities for fellowship and additional teaching.

name: Michael Naas
review: Great place to worship. We found it to be joyful, reverent, and God honoring.

name: Marilyn Hammond
review: Pastor Gleason is the best come and worship with us

name: Matthew Bigelow
review: The people are great, the preaching sound.
